        <p class="metadata">Posted by Pádraic Brady (padraic) on 2010-01-08T15:11:03.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>Zend_Filter_StripTags relies on fully formed HTML that MUST have all attributes quoted. A lack of quotes is forbidden for security reasons and such attributes silently deleted from any output as a result.</p>

        </div>
    </div>
